件与节拍（P0）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":25,"content":"  C1 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（写回 exit.condition，非 conditionSummary 假字段）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":26,"content":"  C2 requiredBeats ↔ beat_completed/beat_missing 联动","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":27,"content":"  C3 exitKind / priority 与引擎 enum roundtrip 验收","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":28,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":55,"content":"| 导入导出正式 ZIP 管道 | 列表导入保持现状 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":56,"content":"| 第二幕内容包 | 不扩叙事 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":57,"content":"| 单卡增量 API | 仍整包保存 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"| ExitCondition **完整** and/or/not 嵌套树 UI | v1 仅常用叶子 + always；复杂嵌套另批或 JSON 逃生 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":59,"content":"| Free 卡主编辑入口迁到故事编辑器 | Free 卡真源仍在 `characters/free-cards/` + 角色库 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"### 1.3 与前置里程碑的关系","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":62,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":63,"content":"| 前置 | 关系 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":64,"content":"|------|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":65,"content":"| 第三步 | 读写盘已通；本批修 participants 误用、conf.cards 不同步、condition 假字段 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":66,"content":"| 细化修改 7 | Effect 15 种面板已通；本批补 critical roundtrip、资产 id 真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":67,"content":"| docs/AI 07 | 资源库/条件 DSL/新建包等纳入本批 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":68,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":120,"content":"| entryCardId | 包配置或章节浮窗可 Select 本包 cardId；新建包默认指向首张 story 卡或占位 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":121,"content":"| critical | 读盘保留；投影不丢；Effect 面板 boolean「失败则中止后续」；写回 effect.critical |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":122,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"### 2.4 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（P0）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":124,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":125,"content":"**问题：** 现 `conditionSummary` 仅 UI 人话；写盘用 `base.condition ?? DEFAULT_CONDITION`，改 summary **不改**引擎 condition。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":126,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":127,"content":"**v1 必须：**","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":128,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":134,"content":"| `beat_missing` | 同上 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":135,"content":"| `all_required_beats_completed` | 单选 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":136,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":137,"content":"- 写回 **`exit.condition`** JSON；`conditionSummary` 改为 **派生预览**（可覆盖显示，但不替代 condition）。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":138,"content":"- **禁止** 保存时一律 `DEFAULT_CONDITION` 覆盖作者已选 condition。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":139,"content":"- and/or/not 嵌套：**本轮不做**完整树；复杂条件允许 JSON 逃生块或保留磁盘原 nested 不覆盖。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":140,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":141,"content":"### 2.5 Studio 编辑器锚点","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":197,"content":"|------|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":198,"content":"| 引用角色 + 校验 | `packages/rpg-engine/src/validation/` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":199,"content":"| 卡 CRUD 同步 | `diskBundleGraph.ts`、`packagesFs.server.ts`、`saveStoryPackage_bis.ts` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":200,"content":"| ExitCondition UI | `bis/.../exitList/`、`com/panel/ExitListEditor/` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":201,"content":"| 资源 API | `apps/studioV2/app/api/assets/`、`utils/server/assets/` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":202,"content":"| 条件/资产/入口 | `PackageConfigFloat`、节点/出口面板 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":203,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":207,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":208,"content":"| 能力 | 真源 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":209,"content":"|------|------|","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":210,"content":"| ExitCondition schema | `packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/outcome.ts` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":211,"content":"| Effect 面板 | 细化修改 7 `com/effects/*` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":212,"content":"| 角色库 | `/api/characters` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":213,"content":"| 故事包 IO | `loadStoryPackage_bis` / `saveStoryPackage_bis` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":242,"content":"- [ ] entryCardId 可改且 validate 通过","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"- [ ] effect.critical 保存 roundtrip 不丢","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":244,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":245,"content":"### 出口条件","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":246,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":247,"content":"- [ ] 改条件 UI 后写盘 condition JSON 变化（非仅 summary）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":248,"content":"- [ ] beat_completed 的 beatId 来自 requiredBeats 选项","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":249,"content":"- [ ] 打开旧包保留原有复杂 nested condition（不被 DEFAULT 覆盖）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":250,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":251,"content":"### 角色 / 锚点","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":252,"content":"","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":283,"content":"- 锚点仍仅 conf.participants 子集 / 双轨白名单","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":284,"content":"- 新建卡不写 conf.cards 或不建 s-card.json","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":285,"content":"- 删卡不删磁盘或 conf 不同步","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":286,"content":"- conditionSummary 写盘替代 exit.condition 或保存一律 DEFAULT_CONDITION","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":287,"content":"- critical 保存丢失","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":288,"content":"- MOCK_ASSETS 仍作资源业务真源","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true},{"lineNumber":289,"content":"- validate 失败仍 PUT","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":true}]}],"totalLines":86,"totalMatchedLines":15,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-eb659caf-4479-4d8c-bee6-ed6349a3ce52-2\nfc_9d3acdc2-463e-9b52-93cc-bf33a69863a0_1","startedAtMs":"1784719677467","completedAtMs":"1784719677624"},"model_call_id":"c409cd48-d9a4-4532-91cf-5021d9a3da75-1-ye9h","session_id":"5553ba5b-1321-4e89-b04c-2f1eadf21aad","timestamp_ms":1784719677605}
