{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-fdb527ec-96c9-411d-96a1-ecdf2613f77b-23\nfc_7115c477-e154-938b-842a-6e3c93b13f0f_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","offset":123,"limit":30},"result":{"success":{"content":"### 2.4 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1（P0）\n\n**问题：** 现 `conditionSummary` 仅 UI 人话；写盘用 `base.condition ?? DEFAULT_CONDITION`，改 summary **不改**引擎 condition。\n\n**v1 必须：**\n\n| op | 面板 |\n|----|------|\n| `always` | 单选「始终」 |\n| `outcome_flag` | flag Select（对齐 OutcomeFlagSchema）+ equals 布尔 |\n| `beat_completed` | beatId Select（来自本卡 objectives.requiredBeats + 手填逃生） |\n| `beat_missing` | 同上 |\n| `all_required_beats_completed` | 单选 |\n\n- 写回 **`exit.condition`** JSON；`conditionSummary` 改为 **派生预览**（可覆盖显示，但不替代 condition）。\n- **禁止** 保存时一律 `DEFAULT_CONDITION` 覆盖作者已选 condition。\n- and/or/not 嵌套：**本轮不做**完整树；复杂条件允许 JSON 逃生块或保留磁盘原 nested 不覆盖。\n\n### 2.5 Studio 编辑器锚点\n\n| 行为 | 口径 |\n|------|------|\n| 打开包 | `fetchCharacterDefs()` 全量锚点 |\n| statusLabel | 有卡 → `本包 · N 卡`；无 → `本章未挂卡` |\n| Effect 下拉 | 全库锚点 + 本包卡列表 |\n\n### 2.6 资源真源（P1）\n\n| 项 | 口径 |\n|----|------|","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":294,"fileSize":12906,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md","readRange":{"startLine":123,"endLine":152},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-fdb527ec-96c9-411d-96a1-ecdf2613f77b-23\nfc_7115c477-e154-938b-842a-6e3c93b13f0f_2","startedAtMs":"1784719703925","completedAtMs":"1784719704086"},"model_call_id":"c409cd48-d9a4-4532-91cf-5021d9a3da75-6-ksjy","session_id":"5553ba5b-1321-4e89-b04c-2f1eadf21aad","timestamp_ms":1784719704088}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-fdb527ec-96c9-411d-96a1-ecdf2613f77b-25\nfc_7115c477-e154-938b-842a-6e3c93b13f0f_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/com/panel/ExitListEditor/com/condition/BeatIdConditionFields.tsx"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 出口条件 v1 · beat_completed / beat_missing 子面板。\n\t*/\n\"use client\";\n\nimport type { FC } from \"react\";\nimport { MenuItem, TextField } from \"@mui/material\";\nimport type { ExitCondition } from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\";\n\nexport type BeatIdConditionFieldsProps = {\n\tcondition: Extract<\n\t\tExitCondition,\n\t\t{ op: \"beat_completed\" | \"beat_missing\" }\n\t>;\n\trequiredBeats: readonly string[];\n\tonCommit: (next: ExitCondition) => void;\n};\n\nexport const BeatIdConditionFields: FC<BeatIdConditionFieldsProps> =\n\tfunction BeatIdConditionFields({\n\t\t// condition 是 beat_* 叶子，用于绑定 beatId\n\t\tcondition,\n\t\t// requiredBeats 是本卡必做节拍，用于下拉候选\n\t\trequiredBeats,\n\t\t// onCommit 写回完整 ExitCondition，用于父面板同步 summary\n\t\tonCommit,\n\t}) {\n\t\tconst beatOptions = Array.from(\n\t\t\tnew Set([\n\t\t\t\t...requiredBeats.filter((id) => id.trim() !== \"\"),\n\t\t\t\tcondition.beatId,\n\t\t\t]),\n\t\t).filter((id) => id.length > 0);\n\n\t\treturn (\n\t\t\t<>\n\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了TextField组件，用于 beatId 下拉 */}\n\t\t\t\t<TextField\n\t\t\t\t\tsize=\"small\"\n\t\t\t\t\tfullWidth\n\t\t\t\t\tselect\n\t\t\t\t\tlabel=\"节拍 beatId\"\n\t\t\t\t\tvalue={\n\t\t\t\t\t\tbeatOptions.includes(condition.beatId) ? condition.beatId : \"\"\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t\tonChange={(e) => {\n\t\t\t\t\t\tonCommit({\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\top: condition.op,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbeatId: e.target.value,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\t}}\n\t\t\t\t\thelperText=\"选项来自本卡必做节拍；也可下方手填。\"\n\t\t\t\t>\n\t\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了MenuItem组件，用于清空 beatId */}\n\t\t\t\t\t<MenuItem value=\"\">（未选）</MenuItem>\n\t\t\t\t\t{beatOptions.map((beatId) => (\n\t\t\t\t\t\t// 引用了MenuItem组件，用于 requiredBeats 选项\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<MenuItem key={beatId} value={beatId}>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t{beatId}\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</MenuItem>\n\t\t\t\t\t))}\n\t\t\t\t</TextField>\n\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了TextField组件，用于 beatId 手填逃生 */}\n\t\t\t\t<TextField\n\t\t\t\t\tsize=\"small\"\n\t\t\t\t\tfullWidth\n\t\t\t\t\tlabel=\"beatId 手填\"\n\t\t\t\t\tvalue={condition.beatId}\n\t\t\t\t\tonChange={(e) => {\n\t\t\t\t\t\tonCommit({\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\top: condition.op,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbeatId: e.target.value,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t});\n\t\t\t\t\t}}\n\t\t\t\t\thelperText=\"逃生口：写入未列入 requiredBeats 的 id。\"\n\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t</>\n\t\t);\n\t};\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":80,"fileSize":2086,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/com/panel/ExitListEditor/com/condition/BeatIdConditionFields.tsx","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":80},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-fdb527ec-96c9-411d-96a1-ecdf2613f77b-25\nfc_7115c477-e154-938b-842a-6e3c93b13f0f_4","startedAtMs":"1784719703932","completedAtMs":"1784719704087"},"model_call_id":"c409cd48-d9a4-4532-91cf-5021d9a3da75-6-ksjy","session_id":"5553ba5b-1321-4e89-b04c-2f1eadf21aad","timestamp_ms":1784719704106}
